.description
An easy to use, versatile, yet full featured database program.  Search or
sort on any field, (un)delete records, print mailing labels or envelopes,
get printouts in many formats, scramble files, flag records, and more.
Fields are user-configurable, so bBase can be used to keep track of
addresses, tape or video collections, recipe files, or anything else you
can think of one program does it all! bBaseIII is a greatly enhanced
successor to bBaseII.  An upgrade to bBaseII.  
